body:
Hello {escalation_target},

An issue requires your immediate attention and has been escalated to your level:

🚨 **Escalation Details:**
Issue: {issue_description}
Original assignee: {original_assignee}
Escalation level: {escalation_level}
Escalated by: {escalator}
Escalation time: {escalation_time}

⏰ **Timeline:**
Initial assignment: {initial_assignment_time}
Time in queue: {time_in_queue}
SLA status: {sla_status}

📊 **Impact Assessment:**
Severity: {severity}
Affected systems: {affected_systems}
User impact: {user_impact}
Business impact: {business_impact}

🔍 **Attempted Actions:**
{attempted_actions}

📝 **Escalation Reason:**
{escalation_reason}

⚡ **Required Actions:**
1. Review the issue details and context
2. Assign appropriate resources or take direct action
3. Communicate with stakeholders about resolution timeline
4. Provide updates on progress

📞 **Contacts:**
Original reporter: {original_reporter}
Current assignee: {current_assignee}
Escalated by: {escalator}

Please acknowledge receipt of this escalation and provide an initial response within 1 hour.

Best regards,
Escalation Management System
